verbose_text: By 1 wk, application of sigma1R-ab, AChR M 1 -ab, AChR M 4 -ab, and ChAT-ab significantly attenuated the tenogenic gene expressions induced by Oxo-M and 4-PPBP, including COL-I, COL-III, Tn-C, VIM, TnmD, and Scx (n = 5 per group; p < 0.001).
